        <text x="44" y="49" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Courier New" font-size="13" font-weight="bold" fill="#8b1a1a">ਰੂਹ</text>
        <text x="44" y="59" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Courier New" font-size="5" fill="#1a1008" letter-spacing="0.8">theRuh</text>
        <text x="44" y="72" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Courier New" font-size="4.5" fill="#1a1008" letter-spacing="1">✦ SOUL SPEAKS ✦</text>
