</div>

<!-- ===== FOOTER ===== -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="footer-head">theRuh</div>
      <div class="footer-text">A personal journal of peculiar souls. Written on antique paper in borrowed ink. Every post is a letter sent to a stranger.</div>
